Small & Medium Enterprises Manager (1.0 beta)
----------------------------------

This application has been developed to fit the needs of SME regarding managing the business.

This beta version handles customers, products, orders & billing. The final version will add functionality to these branches and also will be able to handle reporting.

-----------------------------------

######## REQUIREMENTS ########

You should have this soft installed in order to run this application.

	Ruby 1.8.7 at least
	sqlite3

Gems required

	wxruby
	prawn
	sqlite3-ruby


######## FIRST USE REQUIREMENTS ########

Please customize the information shown within the config screen in order to get this application working properly.

Directories such as log, db, bill and img will be created on first run. Take into account that for orders billing you will need to include your enterprise logo within /img folder.

Your database will be backed up every 15 days (actually, the first time you open the application passed 15 days from the last back up). If you want the DB Backup period to be different, please modify DB_BK_DAYS.
